document.full_text: max mirnyi of belarus and canadian daniel nestor beat surprise south american pairing eduardo schwank and colombian juan sebastian cabal 7-6 3-6 6-4 to win the french open doubles title saturday.
document.title: mirnyi and nestor win doubles final in paris
